--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 0.4.0 (2020-07-07)
C: Redesign cron tasks (use Ansible cron module)
C: Remove option 'chrony_check_time_interval'
C: Remove option 'chrony_update_time_interval'
C: Add option 'chrony_check_time_minute' to specify interval (Default: '*/10')
C: Add option 'chrony_update_time_minute' to specify interval (Default: '*/10')

* Version 0.3.0 (2020-06-30)
C: Redesign role to support SELinux

* Version 0.2.5 (2020-02-10)
B: Add missing dependency 'bc'

* Version 0.2.4 (2020-02-10)
B: Fix integer/float expression issue

* Version 0.2.3 (2020-02-10)
B: Use chronyc base unit (in seconds)

* Version 0.2.2 (2020-02-10)
B: Calculate offset in milliseconds instead of seconds

* Version 0.2.1 (2020-02-09)
E: Remove needless Shell command 'tr'

* Version 0.2.0 (2020-02-09)
F: Add support for CentOS 7

* Version 0.1.0 (2020-02-09)
F: Initial release
